Capital Coaches we strongly believe that businesses dont make decisions, people do, and that considering the human experience and impact and within organisations is critical to success. By partnering with your team to align people, performance and profit, we are driven by the prospect of adding substantial value to the businesses that we partner with.</p>\r\n<p>Robin Human Capital provides services to the business sector on practical human capital management. Further we are a member of the HR Coach Network, the largest provider of the Human Resources solutions to the business sector with over 70 offices across Australia.</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label="Owner and Principal of Robin Human Capital." _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#000000" header_text_color="#ea462c"]\r\n\r\n<h1>Owner and Principal of Robin Human Capital</h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="colored-line-left"></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>With 15 years of operational and strategic HR experience, she has a strong understanding of Employee Relations and the Human Resources function. She understands the importance and impact of strong workforce management, and the effect it can have on business success. Aimee has spent her time across a variety of industry sectors, in both Australian and Global Businesses, including Heavy Industry and Manufacturing, Logistics and Ports, Sales and Marketing and Call Centre.</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built="1" custom_padding="50px||50px|" module_id="package" _builder_version="3.0.63" use_background_color_gradient="on" background_color_gradient_start="rgba(234,31,0,0.64)" background_color_gradient_end="rgba(131,0,233,0.26)" background_color_gradient_direction="272deg" background_color_gradient_start_position="40%" background_image="http://localhost:8888/rhc/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/office-notes-notepad-entrepreneur-38556.jpeg" background_blend="multiply"][et_pb_row _builder_version="3.0.47" background_size="initial" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="repeat"][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="Demonstrated Experience in Managing and Advising on" text_orientation="center" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_font_size="51px" header_text_color="#ffffff"]\r\n\r\n<h1>Demonstrated Experience in Managing and Advising on</h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="colored-line-center"></div>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="3.0.47" background_size="initial" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="repeat"][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_text admin_label="Demonstrated Experience in Managing and Advising on" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_font_size="51px" header_text_color="#ffffff"]\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Managing People Risk  including process and policy design and implementation</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Employee Lifecycle  From Employment Conditions and Contracts through to point of Termination.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Performance and Talent Management</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Organisational and Team Design</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Structural and Cultural Change</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Employee Engagement and Communications Programs</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Mergers and offshoring,</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Restructuring, and redundancy programs;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Negotiating union relationships and EBAs;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">and Strategic high-level business partnering.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_text admin_label="Demonstrated Experience in Managing and Advising on" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header