pproach to people management. We understand that Medium Enterprises are constantly reorganising in order to remain competitive and sustainable. Robin Human Capital specialise in three key areas of enterprise; risk containment, the conveyance of culture and performance alignment.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" custom_padding="50px||50px|" module_id="package" _builder_version="3.0.63" use_background_color_gradient="on" background_color_gradient_start="rgba(234,31,0,0.64)" background_color_gradient_end="rgba(131,0,233,0.26)" background_color_gradient_direction="272deg" background_color_gradient_start_position="40%" background_image="http://localhost:8888/rhc/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/man-coffee-cup-pen.jpg" background_blend="multiply"][et_pb_row _builder_version="3.0.47" background_size="initial" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="repeat"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on"][et_pb_text admin_label="How healthy is your business?" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_text_color="#ffffff"]<h1>How healthy is your business?</h1>\n<p></p>\n<div class="colored-line-left"></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Using a targeted diagnostic tool benchmarking across six critical areas such as Internal business systems, People, and Strategy, we can help you understand the health of your business.</p>\n<p>Find out whether your business activity is aligned with your strategy, and if you are actually on track to meet your business goals.</p>\n<p>Contact us now for a complimentary health check before July 30th.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on"][et_pb_text admin_label="How healthy is your business?" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_text_color="#ffffff" custom_margin="||0px|" custom_padding="||0px|"]<h1>Get your FREE Info Package</h1>\n<p></p>\n<div class="colored-line-left"></div>\n<p></p>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_signup mailchimp_list="|none" button_text="SIGN UP" background_color="rgba(255,255,255,0)" form_field_background_color="rgba(0,0,0,0.63)" form_field_text_color="#ffffff" _builder_version="3.0.63" custom_margin="|0px||" custom_padding="0px|||0px" custom_button="on" button_text_color="#ffffff" button_bg_color="rgba(255,255,255,0)" button_border_width="3" button_border_color="#ffffff" button_border_radius="20" button_use_icon="off" button_bg_color_hover="rgba(234,70,44,0.64)" button_border_color_hover="#ea462c"][/et_pb_signup][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" custom_padding="100px|0px|54px|0px" _builder_version="3.0.47"][et_pb_row background_position_1="top_left" background_position_2="top_left" background_repeat_1="no-repeat" background_repeat_2="no-repeat" custom_css_main_1="position: relative;||" custom_css_main_2="position: relative;||" _builder_version="3.0.63"][et_pb_column type="1_3" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="no-repeat" custom_css_main="position: relative;||"][et_pb_team_member name="Aimee Zahorodny" position="Owner and Principal" image_url="http://localhost:8888/rhc/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/az.jpg" facebook_url="#" twitter_url="#" linkedin_url="#" _builder_version="3.0.63" header_font="|on|||" header_font_size="20" header_text_color="#ea462c" body_text_color="#000000" use_border_color="on" custom_padding="40px|40px|40px|40px" custom_css_main_element="box-shadow: 12px 20px 20px 0px rgba(0,0,0,.1);||" custom_css_member_image=" border-radius: 60%;|| overflow: hidden;|| margin-top: -100px;|| box-shadow: 0 0 rgba(0,0,0,.1);||||" custom_css_member_description="padding-right: 20px;||" custom_css_title="padding-top: 50px;||"]<ul>\n<li><span style="color: #000000;">BA Arts (Psychology)</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #000000;">Graduate Diploma Applied Psychology</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #000000;">Master of Human Resource Management (Employee & Industrial Relations)</span></li>\n</ul>\n[/et_pb_team_member][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="2_3" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="no-repeat" custom_css_main="position: relative;||"][et_pb_text admin_label="Our Business" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#000000" header_text_color="#ea462c"]<h1>Our Business</h1>\n<p></p>\n<div class="colored-line-left"></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Robin Human Capital is passionate about partnering with businesses to ensure that your people activity is aligned with business goals, and strategies, by providing business outcomes that minimise your people risk, and maximise performance and profitability. Our services range from one-off, and project based solutions, to working with your leadership team to manage your human capital activities on a regular basis.</p>\n<p>As Human Capital Coaches we strongly believe that businesses dont make decisions, people do, and that considering the human experience and impact and within organisations is critical to success. By partnering with your team to align people, performance and profit, we are driven by the prospect of adding substantial value to the businesses that we partner with.</p>\n<p>Robin Human Capital provides services to the business sector on practical human capital management. Further we are a member of the HR Coach Network, the largest provider of the Human Resources solutions to the business sector with over 70 offices across Australia.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label="Owner and Principal of Robin Human Capital." _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#000000" header_text_color="#ea462c"]<h1>Owner and Principal of Robin Human Capital</h1>\n<p></p>\n<div class="colored-line-left"></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>With 15 years of operational and strategic HR experience, she has a strong understanding of Employee Relations and the Human Resources function. She understands the importance and impact of strong workforce management, and the effect it can have on business success. Aimee has spent her time across a variety of industry sectors, in both Australian and Global Businesses, including Heavy Industry and Manufacturing, Logistics and Ports, Sales and Marketing and Call Centre.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" custom_padding="50px||50px|" module_id="package" _builder_version="3.0.63" use_background_color_gradient="on" background_color_gradient_start="rgba(234,31,0,0.64)" background_color_gradient_end="rgba(131,0,233,0.26)" background_color_gradient_direction="272deg" background_color_gradient_start_position="40%" background_image="http://localhost:8888/rhc/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/office-notes-notepad-entrepreneur-38556.jpeg" background_blend="multiply"][et_pb_row _builder_version="3.0.47" background_size="initial" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="repeat"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on"][et_pb_text text_orientation="center" admin_label="Demonstrated Experience in Managing and Advising on" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_text_color="#ffffff"]<h1>Aimee Has Demonstrated Experience in Managing and Advising on</h1>\n<p></p>\n<div class="colored-line-center"></div>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="3.0.47" background_size="initial" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="repeat"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on"][et_pb_text admin_label="Demonstrated Experience in Managing and Advising on" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_font_size="51px" header_text_color="#ffffff"]<ul>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Managing People Risk  including process and policy design and implementation</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Employee Lifecycle  From Employment Conditions and Contracts through to point of Termination.</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Performance and Talent Management</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Organisational and Team Design</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Structural and Cultural Change</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Employee Engagement and Communications Programs</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Mergers and offshoring,</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Restructuring, and redundancy programs;</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">Negotiating union relationships and EBAs;</span></li>\n<li><span style="color: #ffffff;">and Strategic high-level business partnering.</span></li>\n</ul>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on"][et_pb_text admin_label="Demonstrated Experience in Managing and Advising on" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_font_size="51px" header_text_color="#ffffff"]<p>Aimee has spent her entire career in within HR and organisational psychology, and has an extensive record of success partnering with various stakeholders from executive teams, through to team leaders and unions, to reach positive and sustainable commercial outcomes.</p>\n<p>She has worked with businesses such as Asciano, Patrick Port Logistics, and Aristocrat Technologies, and has held position such as National Human Resource Manager, Industrial Relations Lead, and Stream Lead People and Culture  Business Integration. Aimee is also a qualified Psychologist.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="3.0.47"][et_pb_row _builder_version="3.0.47" background_size="initial" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="repeat"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on"][et_pb_cta title=