ally focused approach to people management. We understand that Medium Enterprises are constantly reorganising in order to remain competitive and sustainable. Robin Human Capital specialise in three key areas of enterprise; risk containment, the conveyance of culture and performance alignment.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" custom_padding="50px||50px|" module_id="package" _builder_version="3.0.63" use_background_color_gradient="on" background_color_gradient_start="rgba(234,31,0,0.64)" background_color_gradient_end="rgba(131,0,233,0.26)" background_color_gradient_direction="272deg" background_color_gradient_start_position="40%" background_image="http://localhost:8888/rhc/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/man-coffee-cup-pen.jpg" background_blend="multiply"][et_pb_row _builder_version="3.0.47" background_size="initial" background_position="top_left" background_repeat="repeat"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on"][et_pb_text admin_label="How healthy is your business?" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_font_size="25px" header_text_color="#ffffff"]<h1>How healthy is your business?</h1>\n<p></p>\n<div class="colored-line-left"></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Using a targeted diagnostic tool benchmarking across six critical areas such as Internal business systems, People, and Strategy, we can help you understand the health of your business.</p>\n<p>Find out whether your business activity is aligned with your strategy, and if you are actually on track to meet your business goals.</p>\n<p>Contact us now for a complimentary health check before July 30th.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="3.0.47" parallax="off" parallax_method="on"][et_pb_text admin_label="How healthy is your business?" _builder_version="3.0.63" text_text_color="#ffffff" header_font_size="25px" header_text_color="#ffffff" custom_margin="||0px|" custom_padding